Hospital Performance Dashboard

 Project Overview

This project is an interactive Hospital Performance Dashboard developed using Power BI and Microsoft Excel. The dashboard provides insights into hospital performance by analyzing key healthcare metrics such as patient volume, patient satisfaction, average waiting time, and bed occupancy.

🛠️ Tools Used

* Microsoft Power BI
* Microsoft Excel

📊 Dashboard Pages

* Cover Page
* Executive Overview
* Department Analysis
* Hospital Analysis

📈 Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

* Total Patients
* Average Patient Satisfaction
* Average Waiting Time
* Average Bed Occupancy

✨ Dashboard Features

* Interactive KPI Cards
* Bar Charts
* Donut Chart
* Interactive Slicers
* Multi-page Navigation
* Professional Dashboard Design

